  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automated telemetry capture from Claude Code and Cursor via hooks and MCP",
    "Candidate key system for distributing and tracking assessments",
    "Decision capture — candidates document architecture rationale in real time",
    "Derived signals that evaluate prompt depth, verification intensity, error recovery, and more",
    "Session timeline with immutable event log for reviewer auditing",
    "Cohort statistics and percentile rankings across assessment sessions",
    "CLI tools: start, done, explain, status, doctor",
    "Dual authentication: Clerk JWT for reviewers, API keys for candidates"
  ],
